Class LongMemArrayQuickSorter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.internal.util.sort.QuickSorter

  • public class LongMemArrayQuickSorter
extends MemArrayQuickSorter
    QuickSorter implementation for a memory block which stores an array of ints. Memory is accessed using the provided MemoryAccessor.
